    "Finally, as the regulation space and technology use evolve, we cannot exclude the emergence of additional risks associated to LLM usage that we did not anticipate at the time of writing.",
    "reinforcement learning (from manual red teaming and human feedback) to facilitate multi-turn adversarial probing.",
    "Persuasive Adversarial Prompts (PAP) (Zeng et al., 2024a) develops a persuasion taxonomy and employs persuasion technique to jailbreak where an attacker LLM tries to make the request sound more convincing according to persuasive strategy.",
